## API Endpoints

### Workflow Management
- `POST /api/v1/workflows` - Create workflow
- `GET /api/v1/workflows/{id}` - Get workflow details
- `PUT /api/v1/workflows/{id}` - Update workflow
- `DELETE /api/v1/workflows/{id}` - Delete workflow
- `POST /api/v1/workflows/{id}/activate` - Activate workflow
- `POST /api/v1/workflows/{id}/deactivate` - Deactivate workflow

### Workflow Execution
- `POST /api/v1/workflows/{id}/execute` - Execute workflow
- `GET /api/v1/workflows/{id}/executions` - List executions
- `GET /api/v1/workflows/{id}/executions/{execution_id}` - Get execution status
- `POST /api/v1/workflows/{id}/executions/{execution_id}/cancel` - Cancel execution

### Templates
- `GET /api/v1/workflows/templates/list` - List templates
- `POST /api/v1/workflows/templates/{id}/create` - Create from template

### Analytics
- `GET /api/v1/workflows/{id}/statistics` - Get workflow statistics

## Workflow Examples

### Example 1: Simple Approval Workflow

```json
{
  "name": "Document Approval",
  "description": "Approve documents with email notifications",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "start",
      "type": "start",
      "name": "Start"
    },
    {
      "id": "approval",
      "type": "approval",
      "name": "Manager Approval",
      "config": {
        "approvers": ["manager@company.com"],
        "required_approvals": 1
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "email",
      "type": "email",
      "name": "Send Notification",
      "config": {
        "recipients": ["requester@company.com"],
        "subject": "Document Approved",
        "body": "Your document has been approved."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "end",
      "type": "end",
      "name": "End"
    }
  ],
  "edges": [
    {"source": "start", "target": "approval"},
    {"source": "approval", "target": "email"},
    {"source": "email", "target": "end"}
  ]
}
```

### Example 2: Conditional Workflow

```json
{
  "name": "Order Processing",
  "description": "Process orders based on amount",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "start",
      "type": "start",
      "name": "Start"
    },
    {
      "id": "decision",
      "type": "decision",
      "name": "Check Amount",
      "config": {
        "condition": "context['order_amount'] > 1000"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "high_value",
      "type": "approval",
      "name": "High Value Approval"
    },
    {
      "id": "low_value",
      "type": "task",
      "name": "Auto Process"
    },
    {
      "id": "end",
      "type": "end",
      "name": "End"
    }
  ],
  "edges": [
    {"source": "start", "target": "decision"},
    {"source": "decision", "target": "high_value", "label": "true"},
    {"source": "decision", "target": "low_value", "label": "false"},
    {"source": "high_value", "target": "end"},
    {"source": "low_value", "target": "end"}
  ]
}
```

