## Best Practices

### Workflow Design
1. Keep workflows simple and focused
2. Use meaningful node names
3. Add error handling nodes
4. Test workflows before activation
5. Document workflow purpose

### Performance
1. Minimize API calls in loops
2. Use parallel nodes for independent tasks
3. Set appropriate timeouts
4. Monitor execution metrics
5. Optimize long-running workflows

### Error Handling
1. Add retry logic for transient failures
2. Use decision nodes for error paths
3. Send notifications on failures
4. Log errors for debugging
5. Implement fallback workflows

